        @Quand(value="J\'ouvre une nouvelle fen\u00eatre(\\?)")
 @When(value="I open a new window(\\?)")
public void openNewWindow(List<GherkinStepCondition> conditions)
                                                                                                                    throws FailureException
        Open new window with conditions. Note: after this action, you need use "Given '.....' is opened" openUrlIfDifferent
        Parameters:
        conditions - list of 'expected' values condition and 'actual' values (GherkinStepCondition).
        Throws:
        FailureException - if the scenario encounters a functional error

      • openUrlIfDifferent

        @Lorsque(value="{string} est ouvert(\\?)")
 @Given(value="{string} is opened(\\?)")
public void openUrlIfDifferent(String pageKey,
                                                                                                                   List<GherkinStepCondition> conditions)
                                                                                                            throws TechnicalException,
                                                                                                                   FailureException
        Open Url if different with conditions.
        Parameters:
        pageKey - is the key of page (example: GOOGLE_HOME)
        conditions - list of 'expected' values condition and 'actual' values (GherkinStepCondition).
        Throws:
        TechnicalException - is thrown if you have a technical error (format, configuration, datas, ...) in NoraUi. Exception with "FAIL_MESSAGE_UNABLE_TO_OPEN_APPLICATION" message (with screenshot, with exception)
        FailureException - if the scenario encounters a functional error
